parameters:
The road is gone...!? W-What should I do...!! If I can't get
out, what will happen...!?

It might completely disappear...!! If that happens, both of
us will be trapped inside me...!!

Dying inside the dream of someone I love so much... It's
kind of romantic, isn't it... Hehe... I'm saying something
strange, right?

When you say that... it makes me feel like it's a lovely way
to die... To trap you inside me... together.

But still... I'm a little scared. You'll stay by my side
forever, right...?

It's only natural. If you're not with me... my life up until
now would have been meaningless.

When you're near me, I feel at ease... It makes me want to
laugh, but tears start to well up...

That... I feel the same way too. Hehe, we're a perfect
match, aren't we?
It's already... like time, isn't it?

It's good that we could spend our final moments together.
It's good that I love you.
I also... love you, I'm glad.
Thank you... I love you... Luna...

No, how should I put it... It's just... This happiness that
I wanted to see, it's a little different... It's too
perverse or something... Hmm...

I wanted to experience the feeling of ordinary happiness.
Spending peaceful and harmonious days together... and maybe
even having a child eventually... Kyaa!

I wanted to see something like that! What...! Both of you
feeling a romantic connection to a double suicide is a bit
too mature, don't you think...?!
Ahaha... I see...! Both of you seem determined to die...

Show me happiness by saving me forcefully! If that's the
case, I have no choice but to become happy...!

Hmm... For two people, huh... It's a bit heavy, but I guess
it can't be helped...

Ugh... Both of you are so demanding... Making a child do
this kind of labor... It's a crime, you know...!

Okay, this should be good...! I just need to throw it
randomly, right?!

\SE[54]I-I can't go any further...! Let's hurry and turn
back! \SE[53]
